Underஅtheஅgoldenஅhazeஅofஅaஅlateஅafternoonஅsun,அyoungஅEliasஅboundedஅacrossஅtheஅemeraldஅexpanseஅofஅtheஅmeadow,அhisஅredஅballஅclutchedஅtightlyஅinஅhisஅsmall,அdirt-streakedஅhands.அTheஅball,அglossyஅandஅvibrantஅasஅaஅripeஅapple,அbouncedஅwithஅaஅrhythmicஅthudஅagainstஅtheஅearth,அeachஅtossஅsendingஅitஅsoaringஅinஅaஅperfectஅarcஅbeforeஅitஅreturnedஅtoஅhisஅeagerஅgrasp.அBesideஅhim,அhisஅpuppy,அaஅscruffyஅbundleஅofஅcaramelஅfurஅnamedஅPip,அyippedஅwithஅuncontainableஅjoy,அhisஅtinyஅlegsஅaஅblurஅasஅheஅchasedஅtheஅball’sஅerraticஅpath.அPip’sஅearsஅfloppedஅwildly,அcatchingஅtheஅbreeze,அandஅhisஅtongueஅlolledஅout,அpaintingஅtheஅairஅwithஅgleefulஅbarksஅthatஅechoedஅacrossஅtheஅfield.அEliasஅlaughed,அaஅsoundஅasஅbrightஅasஅtheஅdandelionsஅdottingஅtheஅgrass,அhisஅfreckledஅfaceஅalightஅwithஅtheஅpure,அunburdenedஅdelightஅofஅchildhood.அTheஅmeadowஅstretchedஅendlesslyஅbeforeஅthem,அframedஅbyஅancientஅoaksஅwhoseஅleavesஅwhisperedஅsecretsஅinஅtheஅwind,அandஅtheஅworldஅfeltஅvast,அalive,அandஅentirelyஅtheirs.அWithஅaஅplayfulஅgrin,அEliasஅhurledஅtheஅballஅfartherஅthanஅever,அwatchingஅitஅsailஅoverஅaஅlowஅhill,அPipஅscramblingஅafterஅitஅwithஅaஅdeterminedஅyelp.அButஅasஅtheஅpuppyஅvanishedஅoverஅtheஅrise,அaஅstrange,அshimmeringஅlightஅeruptedஅfromஅtheஅspotஅwhereஅtheஅballஅhadஅlanded—aஅradiantஅpulseஅofஅblueஅandஅgoldஅthatஅrippledஅlikeஅwaterஅinஅtheஅair.அEliasஅfroze,அhisஅheartஅthumping,அasஅtheஅlightஅcoalescedஅintoஅaஅglowing,அtranslucentஅfigure,அhumanoidஅyetஅotherworldly,அholdingஅhisஅredஅballஅaloft.அPip,அundaunted,அbarkedஅfuriouslyஅatஅtheஅapparition,அbutஅEliasஅcouldஅonlyஅstare,அhisஅbreathஅcaughtஅinஅhisஅthroat,அasஅtheஅfigure’sஅluminousஅeyesஅmetஅhisஅownஅandஅaஅvoice,அsoftஅasஅstarlight,அwhispered,அYou’veஅfoundஅit.அTheஅmeadow,அonceஅsoஅfamiliar,அnowஅhummedஅwithஅanஅelectricஅmystery,அandஅElias,அclutchingஅPip’sஅcollar,அrealizedஅtheirஅsimpleஅgameஅhadஅstumbledஅintoஅsomethingஅfarஅbeyondஅtheஅordinary.நInஅtheஅheartஅofஅaஅsun-dappledஅpark,அwhereஅwildflowersஅswayedஅlikeஅaஅchorusஅofஅtinyஅdancers,அten-year-oldஅFinnஅdartedஅthroughஅtheஅgrass,அhisஅredஅballஅblazingஅlikeஅaஅcomet