atஅhisஅside,அasஅtheஅordinaryஅworldஅtiltedஅtowardஅtheஅextraordinary.நInஅtheஅgoldenஅglowஅofஅaஅlateஅsummerஅmorning,அwhereஅsunlightஅspilledஅlikeஅhoneyஅoverஅtheஅrollingஅhills,அtwelve-year-oldஅJasperஅracedஅthroughஅaஅmeadowஅburstingஅwithஅwildflowers,அhisஅredஅballஅaஅfieryஅorbஅclutchedஅinஅhisஅcallousedஅhands.அTheஅball,அglossyஅandஅwornஅfromஅcountlessஅgames,அgleamedஅasஅifஅlitஅfromஅwithin,அitsஅscarletஅsurfaceஅscarredஅwithஅtheஅmemoriesஅofஅmuddyஅfieldsஅandஅjoyfulஅtumbles.அBesideஅhim,அhisஅpuppy,அaஅshaggyஅmuttஅnamedஅSparrowஅwithஅeyesஅlikeஅpolishedஅamber,அboundedஅthroughஅtheஅtallஅgrass,அherஅpatchworkஅfurஅcatchingஅburrsஅandஅpetalsஅalike.அSparrow’sஅbarks,அsharpஅandஅexuberant,அrangஅoutஅlikeஅbells,அharmonizingஅwithஅtheஅlazyஅdroneஅofஅbeesஅandஅtheஅwhisperஅofஅaஅbreezeஅthatஅcarriedஅtheஅscentஅofஅcloverஅandஅdistantஅrain.அJasper’sஅlaughter,அwildஅandஅunrestrained,அeruptedஅasஅheஅspun,அtossingஅtheஅballஅinஅaஅhigh,அspiralingஅarc,அwatchingஅitஅsoarஅaboveஅtheஅseaஅofஅgreen.அSparrowஅleaped,அherஅsmallஅbodyஅaஅblurஅofஅmotion,அchasingஅtheஅballஅwithஅaஅdeterminationஅthatஅmadeஅherஅseemஅtwiceஅherஅsize.அTheஅmeadow,அframedஅbyஅaஅricketyஅwoodenஅfenceஅandஅdottedஅwithஅancientஅstonesஅhalf-buriedஅinஅtheஅearth,அpulsedஅwithஅtheஅsimpleஅmagicஅofஅaஅperfectஅday.அWithஅaஅmischievousஅflickஅofஅhisஅwrist,அJasperஅsentஅtheஅballஅrollingஅdownஅaஅgentleஅslopeஅtowardஅaஅclusterஅofஅgnarledஅappleஅtrees,அtheirஅbranchesஅheavyஅwithஅfruit.அSparrowஅtoreஅafterஅit,அvanishingஅintoஅtheஅdappledஅshade.அAஅheartbeatஅlater,அaஅlow,அresonantஅboomஅshudderedஅthroughஅtheஅground,அandஅtheஅairஅbeneathஅtheஅtreesஅshimmeredஅlikeஅheatஅrisingஅfromஅasphalt.அJasperஅfroze,அhisஅpulseஅhammering,அasஅaஅriftஅofஅblindingஅwhiteஅlightஅtoreஅopenஅwhereஅtheஅballஅhadஅstopped—aஅjaggedஅtearஅinஅreality,அpulsingஅwithஅveinsஅofஅsapphireஅandஅviolet.அFromஅwithinஅcameஅaஅgustஅofஅfrigidஅair,அcarryingஅtheஅfaintஅsoundஅofஅchimesஅandஅsomethingஅelse,அaஅlowஅmurmurஅlikeஅvoicesஅspeakingஅinஅaஅtongueஅheஅcouldn’tஅgrasp.அSparrow,அtheஅballஅforgottenஅatஅherஅpaws,அgrowledஅsoftly,அherஅhacklesஅraisedஅasஅsheஅ